/*To make your website fully responsive, you need to add a media query so that the grid changes on smaller screens.

Right now:

3 per row = perfect on laptop
But on a phone 3 per row = too tight

So we add:

Tablet layout â†’ 2 per row
Phone layout â†’ 1 per row */
/* Tablet (max-width 900px) */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .products {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

/* Mobile (max-width 600px) */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .products {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
